title._content: Flocks of Blue Geese and Snow Stop at the Squaw Creek National Wildlife Refuge near Mound City, Missouri...10/1974

description._content: Original Caption: Flocks of Blue Geese and Snow Stop at the Squaw Creek National Wildlife Refuge near Mound City, Missouri, at the Northwest Corner of the State.
